data.title: What is the best place to live between Alberta and Saskatchewan? With the cheapest cost of living, higher wages and best cultural life?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 5): Saskatchewan is cheaper. But that is because in every other way, Alberta is better. While Saskatchewan is still a good place it does not have as diversified an economy as Alberta.
